Q:1  And/Or Operator Java
Send Feedback
Please select the correct statement(s) about && and || operators.

ANS----->
      B] (a || b) && c is true if c is true and either a or b is true
      C] a || b is true if either a or b is true
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------


Q:2  If & Else Java
Send Feedback
Find the output.
int p = 100;
if(p > 20) {
    if(p < 20) {
        System.out.print("coding");
    }
} else {
    System.out.print("ninjas");
}

ANS------>

       D]  No Output
         
