Q:3  Guess the output
Send Feedback
class Output {
    public static void main(String args[]) 
    {    
         int x , y = 1;
         x = 10;
         if (x != 10 && x / 0 == 0)
             System.out.println(y);
         else
             System.out.println(++y);
    } 
}

ANS-------->

         A]  2

